node.text: Trying to bring some laughter on a stressful election night. I present...Paul’s mom at virtual parent teacher conferences. Paul has opted to learn at home this year. Enjoy!

node.text:
The only thing I like about teaching is the kids soooo it’s gonna be a “no” from me dawg. The only other school gig I’d be interested in is counseling. What about you? Leave it in the comments!
.
.
